Python library for unsupervised training of Deep Restricted Bolztmann Machines using three different approaches.

MIT license.

Adding command line args
In order to add command line arguments:
1. Add the argument name as key in dictionary at top of RBM.py, add the default value at the argument type as keys
2. Can then access the argument in main function using: args['arg-name']
To add command line flag:
1. Add name of flag and default value to flag dictionary at top of RBM.py
2. Can access flag as args['flag-name']
